# agent-delivery-kit

- Primary instructions: root `AGENTS.md`, then `product.yaml`.
- Default is **code-first**: complete `docs/code-quality-prerequisites.md` before coding; do not drive task/issue state machines unless the user asks for delivery/status/gates.
- When the user requests closed-loop delivery (`交付`, `顺序完成`, release): follow `docs/delivery-workflow.md`, update front matter + handoff, and run `ruby scripts/deliver.rb <task>`.
- Prove behavior with local checks; never report an assumed pass.
- Preserve unrelated user changes; never discard work silently to resolve conflicts.
- Short commands: `COMMANDS.md`.
